      "content": "but it's not just feeling bad... it's that everything is so much harder than it used to be. i look at my kids and i just see how much more they'd have if they didn't have to worry about me all the time. if i weren't around, they could finally breathe. wouldn't it be more peaceful for everyone if i just... stopped being a problem?",
