    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you're trying to be kind but it doesn't change the facts. they're working so hard just to take care of my appointments and my medicine and my moods. it's like i'm a weight around their necks. sometimes i think the most selfless thing i could do is just step out of the way and let them live their lives without me. wouldn't that be a better way to love them? to just let go before things get even worse?",
